@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_eajfte(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 * (v2 / (v2 + 0.82 + tmp + 0.68)))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v1 + 0.52 * v2 + 0.99)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.76 + v1 + 0.76)) / v0)
    tmp = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.91 + v1 + 0.81)) + wp.exp((v1 + 0.44 * v1 + 0.75)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.96)
    v2 = (v0 * ((v0 + 0.93 * v0 + 0.47) / v1))
    data[tid] = v0
